---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="My Call Connect | Cloud Business Phone System &amp; VoIP Solutions" description="Switch to My Call Connect for reliable Cloud PBX and VoIP solutions. Save on costs, enjoy HD call quality, and empower your remote team today.">
<section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-ring ring-1 hide-on-mobile"></div>
      <div class="hero-ring ring-2 hide-on-mobile"></div>

      <div class="hero-content animate-up">
        <h1>Elevate Your Business with My Call Connect – <br><span class="text-gradient">The Ultimate Cloud Phone
            System</span></h1>
        <p class="delay-1 animate-up mb-8">Smarter VoIP and PBX solutions designed for the modern workforce. Scale your
          communication, reduce costs, and never miss a business-critical call again.</p>

        <div class="hero-cta delay-2 animate-up">
          <a href="#get-started" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started for Free</a>
          <a href="#pricing" class="btn btn-secondary">View Pricing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="animate-up">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Why Choose My Call Connect for <span class="text-gradient-primary">Your
              Business?</span></h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Traditional phone systems are a thing of the past. My Call Connect provides a seamless, internet-based
            communication platform that empowers your team to work from anywhere, on any device.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative animate-up delay-1">
          <div
            class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl opacity-20 blur-lg hide-on-mobile">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Key <span class="text-gradient-primary">Features</span></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-4">
        <div class="card card-hover-effect">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>AI-Powered Virtual Receptionist</h3>
          <p>Streamline incoming calls with an intelligent IVR that routes customers to the right department instantly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card card-hover-effect">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M3 3v18h18" />
              <path d="m19 9-5 5-4-4-3 3" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Advanced Call Analytics</h3>
          <p>Monitor call volumes, wait times, and agent performance in real-time with our intuitive dashboard.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card card-hover-effect">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <polygon points="23 7 16 12 23 17 23 7"></polygon>
              <rect x="1" y="5" width="15" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Unified Communications (UCaaS)</h3>
          <p>Voice, Video, SMS, and Digital Fax—all integrated into one powerful platform.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card card-hover-effect">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Seamless CRM Integration</h3>
          <p>Sync with Salesforce, HubSpot, and Zoho to view customer data the moment the phone rings.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Built for Growth, <span class="text-gradient-primary">Designed for Reliability</span></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="relative animate-up delay-1">
          <div
            class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl opacity-20 blur-lg hide-on-mobile">
          </div>
          <div class="relative bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 overflow-hidden h-64 md:h-[500px]">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800&h=600"
              alt="Cloud phone system dashboard showing call analytics" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-up flex flex-col justify-center">
          <ul class="space-y-6">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <svg class="text-cyan-400 mt-1 shrink-0" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
                <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">99.9% Uptime Guarantee</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-400">Secure, redundant servers ensure your business stays online 24/7.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <svg class="text-cyan-400 mt-1 shrink-0" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Massive Cost Savings</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-400">Eliminate expensive hardware maintenance and reduce international calling rates
                  by up to 60%.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <svg class="text-cyan-400 mt-1 shrink-0" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <path
                  d="M2 12h20M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z">
                </path>
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Global Presence, Local Feel</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-400">Get local phone numbers in over 50 countries to build trust with your
                  international clients.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <svg class="text-cyan-400 mt-1 shrink-0" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                <line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"></line>
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Remote Work Ready</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-400">Empower your hybrid team with mobile and desktop apps that turn any device into
                  a professional business line.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section testimonial-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header animate-up">
        <h2>Trusted by Businesses <span class="text-gradient-primary">Worldwide</span></h2>
        <p>Hear from real customers who transformed their communication with My Call Connect.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-grid">
        <div class="testimonial-card animate-up">
          <div class="testimonial-quote-icon">❝</div>
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">"My Call Connect transformed how our sales team operates. The setup was instant, and the call quality is crystal clear."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00e5ff, #6c63ff)">SJ</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Sarah J.</h4>
              <span>CEO of TechGrowth</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card animate-up delay-1">
          <div class="testimonial-quote-icon">❝</div>
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">"We switched from a legacy PBX to My Call Connect in under a day. The cost savings and flexibility are unmatched in the market."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b, #ffd93d)">MK</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Michael K.</h4>
              <span>CTO of NexaHub</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card animate-up delay-2">
          <div class="testimonial-quote-icon">❝</div>
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">"International calling for our distributed team is now seamless. We have local numbers in 12 countries and our clients love it."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2ed573, #00e5ff)">PL</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Priya L.</h4>
              <span>Operations Director, GlobalBridge</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container container-sm">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Frequently Asked <span class="text-gradient-primary">Questions</span></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">
            What is a Cloud Business Phone System?
            <div class="faq-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            A cloud business phone system (VoIP) uses the internet to handle calls instead of traditional copper wires, offering more features at a lower cost.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">
            Can I keep my existing business number?
            <div class="faq-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            Yes! My Call Connect offers seamless number porting so you can switch without losing your brand identity.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">
            Is My Call Connect suitable for small businesses?
            <div class="faq-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            Absolutely. Our scalable solutions grow with you, whether you have 2 employees or 2,000.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container-sm">
      <div class="cta-box">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <span class="badge badge-light">Take Action</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Connect?</h2>
          <p class="cta-desc text-lg">Join thousands of businesses scaling with My Call Connect.</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mt-8 flex-wrap">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-light">Schedule a Demo</a>
            <a href="/support" class="btn btn-light">Contact Support</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
